{"tid":1139391,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"石壁監獄服刑　戴耀廷球場跑步","createTime":"2019-05-05T08:35:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T09:45:53.000Z","uid":224066,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"370bfd86e22b8f9b24469aed0276fe652cc3765f","tid":1139391,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T08:35:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505112806166-0505_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190505160734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505112806166-0505_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190505160734&h=13882007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n違法佔領行動(佔中)案中判囚16個月的香港大學法律系副教授戴耀廷，目前在大嶼山石壁監獄服刑。東網記者今早(5日)約11時前拍得戴耀廷在獄中「放風」期間，在足球場緩步跑。戴身穿藍色上衣及短褲，不時以毛巾抹汗，全程跑了約半小時，大約跑了十多個圈，兩名懲教人員離遠觀察，亦引起其他同在「放風」的在囚人士注目。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505112806166-0505_00822_001_02b.jpg?20190505160734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505112806166-0505_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20190505160734&h=a772dc8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佔中發起人戴耀廷、陳健民、朱耀明上月底就佔中案被法庭判刑。戴及陳分別被判囚16個月，朱則被判監16個月，緩刑2年。其中戴耀廷上月29日在懲教署人員安排下轉送往大嶼山石壁監獄<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190505/photo/bkn-20190505112806166-0505_00822_001_03b.jpg?20190505160734\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190505%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190505112806166-0505_00822_001_03b.jpg%3F20190505160734&h=2657b9ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4fda222e4805765745bb61edc6848bc1944f9c4","tid":1139391,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:07:10.000Z","msg":"點解佢唔洗著啡色囚衣"},{"pid":"7c4100c99142e38c601ca9b5cd37107f0fdb14ed","tid":1139391,"uid":192409,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-05T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"有份高尚 穩定職業都唔怕犧牲一切 敢企黎抗爭 仲搞到坐監 其實好難得"},{